**Key features:**
- Uses OKLCH color space for modern color handling
- Includes light and dark mode themes
- Defines semantic color tokens (primary, secondary, accent, destructive, etc.)
- Defines radius tokens for component border-radius
- Maps chart colors (1-5)
- Includes sidebar-specific color tokens

